{"type":"message","id":"c0c1a386","parentId":"c4343e12","timestamp":"2026-03-21T02:19:08.724Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到这是一张机械臂产品包装箱的照片，显示的是慧手科技（Hiwonder）的 LeRobot 机械臂套件。\n\n照片上显示了：\n- 主臂和从臂的示意图\n- 配件清单（单目相机、相机支架、USB 数据线、配件包等）\n- 使用注意事项\n- 课程资料链接：https://www.hiwonder.com.cn/course-detail/LeRobot.html\n- 技术支持邮箱：support@hiwonder.com\n\n这是你新买的机械臂吗？🦾 需要我帮你查什么信息吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":828,"output":128,"cacheRead":13571,"cacheWrite":99,"totalTokens":14626,"cost":{"input":0.00009108,"output":0.00003584,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00012692}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774059544525}}
